      <section id="about">
        <div class="text">
          <h1 class="title">About</h1>
          <p class="black">
            The big picture is ultimately about people. Likewise, Big Picture Consulting is
            also about people.
            <br><br>
            We are a Charlotte-based management consulting firm that helps leaders see their big picture.
            Our purpose is to assess and transform organizations into highly effective teams. We work with mid-market business leaders and C-level executives to shape strategy, enhance
            operations, and make substantial, lasting performance improvements. We serve a broad and constantly expanding range of industries from financial firms
            and residential and commercial service contractors, to manufacturers, retailers and
            medical and dental practices.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/about"><button class="moreBtn blueBtn">Continue Reading</button></a>
        </div>
        <div class="img"></div>
      </section>
      <section id="services">
        <div class="img"></div>
        <div class="text">
          <h1 class="title">Services</h1>
          <p class="black">
            All of our services are custom tailored to fit the unique needs and goals of our
            clients. Whether your organization earns $1 million or $100 million in annual revenues,
            or has 100 or 1000 employees, our work always revolves around clearly defining your big
            picture, charting a course, streamlining roles, and strengthening operations.
            <br><br>
            We offer full-scope and limited-scope assessments of your organization, strategic
            planning, profit planning and cost control installation, revenue growth and marketing
            planning, dashboard design and installation for monitoring purposes, organizational
            development and change, leadership coaching and more.
            <br>
          </p>
          <a href="/services"><button class="moreBtn blueBtn">Learn More</button></a>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section id="testimonials">
        <div class="text">
          <h1 class="title">What Others Are Saying</h1>
          <p class="black">At the conclusion of each project the owner of BPC, Glenn Love, invites clients to share their opinions about the services they received. Below are some statements shared by some of the CEOs and business owners Glenn has assisted over the years.</p>
          <p
            class="black">
            <blockquote><i>"The amount of time I was spending at the office was increasing while the profits of the business were making were decreasing. Glenn came in and helped me re-organize the entire company so that now I delegate tasks to a handful of department ..."</i></blockquote>
          </p><a href="/testimonials"><button class="moreBtn blueBtn">Continue Reading</button></a></div>
        <div class="img"></div>
      </section>
      <section id="faq">
        <div class="img">
          <h1 class="titleOnImg">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="text black"><span class="answer"><b>Q:</b></span> How do I know that any information I would share with you would be held in strict confidence?<br><br><span class="answer"><b>A:</b></span> Any consultants who work on BPC projects are required to sign the Engagement
          Agreement which contains a strict confidentiality and non-disclosure clause. BPC works hard to gain your trust and takes these issues extremely seriously in order to maintain your trust.<br><br>
          <hr><br><span class="answer"><b>Q:</b></span> How much are your fees?<br><br><span class="answer"><b>A:</b></span> That depends on the scope and depth of the work we do, the size of your organization, the number of employees you have, the complexity
          of the project, and a variety of other factors that must be considered. Before any work is done, the work required is carefully defined and put in writing, all phases of the project are outlined in writing, and the fee to be charged for each phase
          is provided. There are no surprises and no undisclosed add-ons (i.e., no "change orders") without prior discussion and prior written consent from the client.<br><br><a href="/faq"><button id="expandFaq" class="moreBtn blueBtn">See all FAQs</button></a></div>
      </section>
      <section id="contact">
        <h1 class="title">Connect</h1>
        <p class="text black">If you have any questions or wish to request a free, one-hour consultation with Glenn Love, the owner and president of BPC, please submit the form below and he will get back to you as soon as possible. Thank you.<br><br> Big Picture Consulting<br>        Charlotte, NC<br><br> Glenn Love<br> Email: <a href="mailto:glenn@bigpicture.life">glenn@bigpicture.life</a><br> Phone: <a href="tel:7043096285">704-309-6285</a></p>

        <form id="contactForm" action="/contact" method="post" class="text">
          <input type="text" name="firstName" placeholder="First Name*" autocomplete="given-name" required><br>
          <p class="formError" id="firstNameError">Please fill out this field</p>
          <input type="text" name="lastName" placeholder="Last Name*" autocomplete="family-name" required><br>
          <p class="formError" id="lastNameError">Please fill out this field</p>
          <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email*" autocomplete="email" required><br>
          <p class="formError" id="emailError">Please enter a valid email address</p>
          <input type="email" name="email2" placeholder="Confirm Email*" autocomplete="email" required><br>
          <p class="formError" id="email2Error">Email address does not match</p>
          <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone" autocomplete="tel-national"><br>
          <p class="formError" id="phoneError">Please enter a valid US phone number</p>
          <input type="text" name="orgName" placeholder="Organization Name" autocomplete="organization"><br>
          <input type="number" name="orgZIP" placeholder="Organization ZIP Code" autocomplete="postal-code"><br>
          <p class="formError" id="orgZIPError">Please enter a valid US ZIP code</p>
          <datalist id="referrers">
            <option value="From a friend"></option>
            <option value="Twitter"></option>
            <option value="LinkedIn"></option>
          </datalist>
          <input type="text" list="referrers" name="referrer" placeholder="How did you hear about us?">
          <input type="text" name="subject" placeholder="Subject*" required><br>
          <p class="formError" id="subjectError">Please fill out this field</p>
          <textarea type="text" name="message" placeholder="Message*" required></textarea><br>
          <p class="formError" id="messageError">Please fill out this field</p>
          <input id="optOut" type="checkbox" name="optOut">
          <label for="optOut" class="black">I would like to opt out of subscribing to the Big Picture blog</label><br><br>
          <input type="hidden" id="hidden" name="recaptcha">
          <button
            id="formSubmit"
            class="ghostBtn g-recaptcha hidden"
            data-sitekey="6LclwTcUAAAAAE_77bXHeJku9IJh1v8dCTVnHtUB"
            data-badge="inline"
            data-callback='onRecaptcha'>Send
          </button>
          <button id="fakeSubmit" class="ghostBtn blueBtn">Send</button>
        </form>

      </section>
